body:
@micklexqg If I am understanding it correctly then you are mentioning `tensorflow-gpu 1.1.x` which must have cuda support along with specific .dll.
Also,you are using two different versions of tensorflow-gpu for windows 7 and windows 10!
From screenshot it seems tensor flow is not recognizing the some attributes which might be different in two versions of 1.1.0 and 1.0.1
Please follow template [here](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/ISSUE_TEMPLATE.md) along with your source code in order to get things clear!
